name: Mini Store
body:
### Welcome to Mini Store
This project is to build mini online store. 

### Skill Used
`MongoDB` `Express` `AngularJS` `Node.JS`

### User page
User page shows the list of user registered.

### Product Page
Product Page shows the product with image and remaining number.

### Order Page
In order page, you can select product and number of product to buy.
